{
  "name": "Helm of Telepathy",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>While wearing this helm, you can use an action to cast the <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.NIy2ukFNVyjrCLf8]{detect thoughts} spell (save DC 13) from it. As long as you maintain &amp;Reference[concentration]{concentration} on the spell, you can use a bonus action to send a telepathic message to a creature you are focused on. It can reply--using a bonus action to do so--while your focus on it continues.</p>\n<p>While focusing on a creature with <strong></strong><strong>detect thoughts</strong>, you can use an action to cast the <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.lA9cDlOhVk3KUbHZ]{suggestion} spell (save DC 13) from the helm on that creature. Once used, the <strong></strong><strong>suggestion</strong> property can't be used again until the next dawn.</p>\n</div>",
